      "message": "wallet, rpc: add include_change parameter to listtransactions\n\nlistsinceblock already supports an include_change parameter, and the\ninternal ListTransactions helper already accepts it. Wire this parameter\nthrough the listtransactions RPC handler for consistency.\n\nThis addresses the issue reported in #34632, where transactions sending\nexclusively to change addresses are silently hidden from listtransactions.",
